22/1 Die_Hard
New_York_City policeman John_Mc Clane ( Bruce_Willis ) is visiting his estranged wife ( Bonnie_Bedelia ) and two daughters on Christmas_Eve . He joins her at a holiday party in the headquarters of the Japanese-owned business she works for . But the festivities are interrupted by a group of terrorists who take over the exclusive high - rise , and everyone in it . Very soon McClane realizes that there ' s no one to save the hostages - - but him
28/1 Hateful_Eight
While racing toward the town of Red_Rock in post - Civil_War_Wyoming , bounty hunter John " The_Hangman " Ruth ( Kurt_Russell ) and his fugitive prisoner ( Jennifer_Jason_Leigh ) encounter another bounty hunter ( Samuel L . Jackson ) and a man who claims to be a sheriff . Hoping to find shelter from a blizzard , the group travels to a stagecoach stopover located on a mountain pass . Greeted there by four strangers , the eight travelers soon learn that they may not make it to their destination after all .
